# Ultimate Click Master

![Game Screenshot](https://via.placeholder.com/800x450?text=Ultimate+Click+Master+Gameplay)

A fast-paced, engaging clicker game built with pure HTML, CSS, and JavaScript, powered by GSAP for smooth animations. Test your reflexes and precision as you aim for the highest score!

## ‚ú® Features

*   **Dynamic Gameplay:** Boxes appear randomly, challenging your reaction time.
*   **Multiple Box Types:**
    *   üîµ **Regular Boxes (+1 Point):** Standard targets.
    *   üü¢ **Bonus Circles (+5 Points, +3 Seconds):** High-value targets that extend your playtime.
    *   üî¥ **Penalty Diamonds (-3 Points, -5 Seconds):** Avoid these! They deduct points and precious time.
*   **Combo System:** Achieve consecutive clicks within a short timeframe to build combos and earn bonus points.
*   **Missed Click Penalty:** Clicking outside the active game box will cost you points and time, encouraging precision.
*   **Visual Feedback:** Animated score and time pop-ups provide immediate feedback on your actions.
*   **Progressive Difficulty:** As your score increases, the game level rises, making boxes move faster and increasing the frequency of challenging penalty boxes.
*   **High Score Tracking:** Your best score is saved locally in your browser, allowing you to compete against yourself.
*   **Clean & Professional UI:** A modern, minimalist design with a white background and subtle gradients for a polished look.
*   **Responsive Design:** Adapts to different screen sizes.

## üéÆ How to Play

1.  **Start the Game:** Click the "Start Game" button on the welcome screen.
2.  **Click the Boxes:** As boxes appear, click them quickly to earn points.
3.  **Identify Box Types:**
    *   Click **Blue Boxes** for standard points.
    *   Prioritize **Green Circles** for bonus points and extra time.
    *   **Avoid Red Diamonds** as they will penalize your score and time.
4.  **Build Combos:** Click rapidly to chain combos and earn additional points.
5.  **Be Precise:** Clicking anywhere on the screen *outside* the game box will result in a penalty.
6.  **Survive:** Keep your time above zero to continue playing.
7.  **Restart:** After the game ends, click "Play Again" to challenge your high score.

## üõ†Ô∏è Technologies Used

*   **HTML5:** Structure of the game.
*   **CSS3:** Styling and visual presentation.
*   **JavaScript (ES6+):** Game logic and interactivity.
*   **GSAP (GreenSock Animation Platform):** For smooth, high-performance animations of game elements.

